Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 of Hip MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Other pathologies' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

And 'Intrapelvin ascites' radio button is enabled
And 'Suspect lymph nodes' radio button is enabled
And 'Not specified intrapelvic mass (need of additional diagnostics)' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Suspect lymph nodes' radio button
Then 'Inguinal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Iliacal' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Inguinal' checkbox
Then 'Max. short axis diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Quantity' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Iliacal' checkbox
Then 'Max. short axis diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Quantity' dropdown menu is enabled
